content:
What are the missing words in the following phrase that, when inserted in the correct order, create a well-known idiom about success? 
"A strong _______ _______ every successful person. Key components to success are motivation and determination. Don't let anything stand in the way of achieving your goals, aim _______." 
Please provide the correct missing words in the correct order to complete the phrase.

The missing words in the phrase are "will," "drives," and "high." When inserted, the complete idiom reads: "A strong will drives every successful person. Key components to success are motivation and determination. Don't let anything stand in the way of achieving your goals, aim high."
